itch","contents":"<div class=\"article-thumb svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/you-actually-need-to-context-switch/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><img src=\"/images/articles/you-actually-need-to-context-switch/you-actually-need-to-context-switch_thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"You Actually Need to Context Switch\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">\n        </a></div>\n      <div class=\"article-info svelte-1fj1tr4\"><div class=\"article-category svelte-1fj1tr4\">Atomic Essay: <span class=\"article-highlight-eyebrow-cat svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/c/productivity/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">Productivity</a></span></div>\n        <div class=\"article-title svelte-1fj1tr4\"><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0em;\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/you-actually-need-to-context-switch/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">You Actually Need to Context Switch</a></h2></div>\n        <div class=\"article-descr svelte-1fj1tr4\">Common wisdom says that you need to avoid context switching. That's only half true – sometimes you need to context switch.\n        </div></div>","link":"https://www.cortexfutura.com/you-actually-need-to-context-switch/","retrieved":1670520895781},{"title":"How to Context Switch Like a Pro","contents":"<div class=\"article-thumb svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/how-to-context-switch-like-a-pro/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><img src=\"/images/articles/how-to-context-switch-like-a-pro/workcycle-example_squashed.jpg\" alt=\"How to Context Switch Like a Pro\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">\n        </a></div>\n      <div class=\"article-info svelte-1fj1tr4\"><div class=\"article-category svelte-1fj1tr4\">Article: <span class=\"article-highlight-eyebrow-cat svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/c/productivity/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">Productivity</a></span></div>\n        <div class=\"article-title svelte-1fj1tr4\"><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0em;\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/how-to-context-switch-like-a-pro/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">How to Context Switch Like a Pro</a></h2></div>\n        <div class=\"article-de