randfather's research technique - Index, Proto-Zettelkasten, Paper\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">\n        </a></div>\n      <div class=\"article-info svelte-1fj1tr4\"><div class=\"article-category svelte-1fj1tr4\">Article: <span class=\"article-highlight-eyebrow-cat svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/c/zettelkasten/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">Zettelkasten</a></span></div>\n        <div class=\"article-title svelte-1fj1tr4\"><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0em;\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/my-grandfathers-research-technique/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">My grandfather's research technique - Index, Proto-Zettelkasten, Paper</a></h2></div>\n        <div class=\"article-descr svelte-1fj1tr4\">My grandfather's way of doing history research before the computer age. Using paper and a meticulous process, he built something close to a Zettelkasten.\n        </div></div>","link":"https://www.cortexfutura.com/my-grandfathers-research-technique/","retrieved":1670520895782},{"title":"How to cure Highlight Dementia","contents":"<div class=\"article-thumb svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/how-to-cure-highlight-dementia/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><img src=\"/images/articles/how-to-cure-highlight-dementia/highlight_dementia_thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"How to cure Highlight Dementia\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">\n        </a></div>\n      <div class=\"article-info svelte-1fj1tr4\"><div class=\"article-category svelte-1fj1tr4\">Article: <span class=\"article-highlight-eyebrow-cat svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/c/reading/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">Reading</a></span></div>\n        <div class=\"article-title svelte-1fj1tr4\"><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0em;\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/how-to-cure-highlight-dementia/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">How to cure Highlight Dementia</a></h2></div>\n        <div class=\"article-descr svelte-1fj1tr4\">How to make sure that you never lose insights when reading and highlighting. Because Highlight Dementia is completely preventable.\n        </div></div>","link":"https: