lass=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">\n        </a></div>\n      <div class=\"article-info svelte-1fj1tr4\"><div class=\"article-category svelte-1fj1tr4\">Article: <span class=\"article-highlight-eyebrow-cat svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/c/algorithm-of-thought/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">Algorithm of Thought</a></span></div>\n        <div class=\"article-title svelte-1fj1tr4\"><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0em;\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/right-to-disagree/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">The Right to Disagree</a></h2></div>\n        <div class=\"article-descr svelte-1fj1tr4\">Contrary to popular belief, you can't just disagree with someone because you feel like it. You have to __earn__ the right to disagree with someone's position.\n        </div></div>","link":"https://www.cortexfutura.com/right-to-disagree/","retrieved":1670520895782},{"title":"A Gruvbox Theme for Roam Research","contents":"<div class=\"article-thumb svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/gruvbox-theme/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><img src=\"/images/articles/gruvbox-theme/gruvbox-light_thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"A Gruvbox Theme for Roam Research\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">\n        </a></div>\n      <div class=\"article-info svelte-1fj1tr4\"><div class=\"article-category svelte-1fj1tr4\">Article: <span class=\"article-highlight-eyebrow-cat svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/c/roam-research/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">Roam Research</a></span></div>\n        <div class=\"article-title svelte-1fj1tr4\"><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0em;\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\"><a href=\"/gruvbox-theme/\" class=\"svelte-1fj1tr4\">A Gruvbox Theme for Roam Research</a></h2></div>\n        <div class=\"article-descr svelte-1fj1tr4\">How to create a Gruvbox-style color theme for Roam Research using Roam's built-in CSS capabilities.\n        </div></div>","link":"https://www.cortexfutura.com/gruvbox-theme/","retrieved":1670520895783}]}